import React from 'react'

const SearchItem = () => {
  return (

    <form className="searchForm" onSubmit={(e)=>e.preventDefault()}>
    <label htmlFor='search'>Search</label>
      <input 
        type="text"
        id="search"
        role='serachBox'
        placeholder='Search Items'
      />

    
    
   </form>
  )
}

export default SearchItem
